 I do that all the time, I call funerals weddings

1341
00:55:25,060 --> 00:55:28,540
 because that's exactly what it is for believers.

1342
00:55:28,540 --> 00:55:31,260
 It's your homecoming, man, your bridegroom's ready.

1343
00:55:31,260 --> 00:55:32,820
 At the end of the funeral,

1344
00:55:32,820 --> 00:55:36,860
 they played a song that I'm about to play for you,

1345
00:55:36,860 --> 00:55:39,940
 and there was in that room a bunch of Navy SEALs.

1346
00:55:39,940 --> 00:55:42,940
 A bunch of others that had graduated from the Academy.

1347
00:55:42,940 --> 00:55:47,740
 And when the song started, it's the Navy alma mater

1348
00:55:47,740 --> 00:55:50,380
 that if you're a graduate of Annapolis, you sing.

1349
00:55:50,380 --> 00:55:54,740
 And they all got up, and there's about 10 of those men

1350
00:55:54,740 --> 00:55:56,540
 that came and stood around the bride.

1351
00:55:56,540 --> 00:56:01,180
 And I remember looking at those guys,

1352
00:56:01,180 --> 00:56:03,180
 and one of my great regrets in life

1353
00:56:03,180 --> 00:56:07,300
 is that I didn't, I didn't know what to do.

1354
00:56:07,300 --> 00:56:09,300
 And one of the great regrets in life

1355
00:56:09,300 --> 00:56:11,700
 is that I didn't serve our country

1356
00:56:11,700 --> 00:56:16,220
 the way godly and faithful, strong men serve our country,

1357
00:56:16,220 --> 00:56:17,740
 strong women serve our country.

1358
00:56:17,740 --> 00:56:19,140
 I never had that as part of my story.

1359
00:56:19,140 --> 00:56:22,080
 And I remember sitting there longing to be a guy

1360
00:56:22,080 --> 00:56:25,100
 that could have stood up with those Navy SEALs

1361
00:56:25,100 --> 00:56:28,540
 and those midshipmen that had sacrificed by the sea

1362
00:56:28,540 --> 00:56:31,380
 to be trained to sail on waters and defeat evil.

1363
00:56:31,380 --> 00:56:35,540
 I want you to put yourself back in that funeral for a second

1364
00:56:35,540 --> 00:56:37,460
 and then I close with the last statements.

1365
00:56:37,460 --> 00:56:38,700
 But this song was played,

1366
00:56:38,700 --> 00:56:40,880
 and imagine getting to stand up when it was done.

