00:56:50,060 --> 00:56:52,180
 And I thought to myself,

1372
00:56:52,180 --> 00:56:54,780
 I serve in a much more noble army than that.

1373
00:56:54,780 --> 00:56:59,300
 And as much as I would have wanted

1374
00:56:59,300 --> 00:57:01,100
 to be through some of the tours,

1375
00:57:01,100 --> 00:57:02,780
 to do that those guys were in the Philippines

1376
00:57:02,780 --> 00:57:05,180
 and Afghanistan and on all the seas,

1377
00:57:05,180 --> 00:57:06,700
 I thought to myself, nope, right now,

1378
00:57:06,700 --> 00:57:07,700
 I'm part of the remnant, man.

1379
00:57:07,700 --> 00:57:10,460
 I am serving something even more noble than that.

1380
00:57:10,460 --> 00:57:16,540
 And when my king at the end of the day is worshiped

1381
00:57:16,540 --> 00:57:21,420
 and the alma mater of the remnant is sung, I will stand.

1382
00:57:21,420 --> 00:57:24,500
 And by the grace of God, as I walk with him,

1383
00:57:24,500 --> 00:57:26,320
 as a soldier who doesn't entangle himself

1384
00:57:26,320 --> 00:57:27,660
 in the affairs of everyday life

