00:57:27,660 --> 00:57:28,980
 in order that I might please the one

1386
00:57:28,980 --> 00:57:31,700
 that enlisted me as a soldier, I will stand.

1387
00:57:31,700 --> 00:57:34,300
 And I will be glad that by the grace of God I have seen,

1388
00:57:34,300 --> 00:57:36,780
 that by the grace of God I served.

1389
00:57:36,780 --> 00:57:41,460
 By the grace of God I spoke in a winsome way

1390
00:57:41,460 --> 00:57:43,580
 with my speech seasoned with salt as it was,

1391
00:57:43,580 --> 00:57:45,040
 and I stood firm.

1392
00:57:45,040 --> 00:57:47,540
 And if I die in flames,

1393
00:57:47,540 --> 00:57:50,300
 I pray that God will use it to light a candle

1394
00:57:50,300 --> 00:57:51,860
 that the entire world will see.

1395
00:57:51,860 --> 00:57:57,220
 There is nothing more noble than being the remnant,

1396
00:57:57,220 --> 00:58:00,780
 when the remnant serves the kind and benevolent

1397
00:58:00,780 --> 00:58:02,900
 and true all powerful king.

1398
00:58:03,740 --> 00:58:07,300
 This world needs a remnant.

1399
