 It is calling cats, dogs, girls, boys, and lies truth.

1400
00:58:13,580 --> 00:58:20,540
 And humans do not flourish under lies.

1401
00:58:20,540 --> 00:58:23,300
 If you by the grace of God have come to know the truth,

1402
00:58:23,300 --> 00:58:26,020
 live as if you know the truth.

1403
00:58:26,020 --> 00:58:31,860
 Speak gently but courageously before any king.

1404
00:58:32,700 --> 00:58:34,820
 Because you stand firm for yours.

1405
00:58:34,820 --> 00:58:36,780
 Let's go.

1406
00:58:36,780 --> 00:58:40,060
 Father, I pray we'd be the remnant.

1407
00:58:40,060 --> 00:58:41,860
 I pray if there's any in here tonight

1408
00:58:41,860 --> 00:58:46,860
 that has had a confusing understanding

1409
00:58:46,860 --> 00:58:49,060
 about what it is that you want from us.

1410
00:58:49,060 --> 00:58:51,900
 If they've been confused to think

1411
00:58:51,900 --> 00:58:53,660
 that they've got to serve long and nobly

1412
00:58:53,660 --> 00:58:56,340
 in order to possibly be admitted into your family,

1413
00:58:56,340 --> 00:58:59,220
 I pray that you would shake them out of that

1414
00:58:59,220 --> 00:59:02,660
 and understand that all you do is call broken sinners

1415
00:59:02,660 --> 00:59:04,300
 and just say, "Are you sick and tired of drowning

1416
00:59:04,300 --> 00:59:06,020
 "in the sea of human despair?

1417
00:59:06,020 --> 00:59:07,340
 "Then come to me.

1418
00:59:07,340 --> 00:59:10,380
 "And I will restore the glory that is lost.

1419
00:59:10,380 --> 00:59:12,100
 "I will make beauty from your ashes.

1420
00:59:12,100 --> 00:59:13,780
 "I'll make you my remnant.

1421
00:59:13,780 --> 00:59:16,940
 "I'll call you out of darkness into my marvelous light.

1422
00:59:16,940 --> 00:59:18,340
 "And I'll make you as a shining star

1423
00:59:18,340 --> 00:59:20,500
 "in the midst of a dark and perverse generation.

1424
00:59:20,500 --> 00:59:22,460
 "I'll put in you a heart of courage.

1425
00:59:22,460 --> 00:59:24,820
 "I'll put in your lips words that are true.

1426
00:59:24,820 --> 00:59:28,740
 "I will clothe you in dignity and honor and compassion

1427
00:59:28,740 --> 00:59:31,300
 "and kindness and boldness.

1428
00:59:31,300 --> 00:59:33,940
 "I will give you the ability to take heart

1429
00:59:33,940 --> 00:59:37,320
 "in the midst of those that seek our life

1430
00:59:37,320 --> 00:59:39,620
 "because you know that this world is not your home."

1431
00:59:39,620 --> 00:59:42,300
 Oh, Father, what a privilege

1432
00:59:42,300 --> 00:59:45,500
 that grace would enlist us in your family.

1433
00:59:45,500 --> 00:59:49,180
 And what a privilege to be shepherded by you as your sheep.

1434
00:59:49,180 --> 00:59:55,340
 Would you help us not just to sing songs,

1435
00:59:55,340 --> 00:59:58,400
 but to have our heart filled with the spirit of truth,

1436
00:59:58,400 --> 01:00:00,200
 that we might be a remnant indeed

1437
01:00:00,200 --> 01:00:02,100
 for the glory of our King until he comes.

1438
01:00:02,100 --> 01:00:05,180
 In Jesus' name, amen.

1439
01:00:05,180 --> 01:00:06,180
 Let's stand together.

